            "@type": "Answer",
            "text": "Spokane has extensive free resources. Apply for Apple Health (Medicaid) at any CHAS clinic for same-day coverage. State-funded treatment is available at STARS and Frontier Behavioral Health. Free shelter is available at Union Gospel Mission, House of Charity, and Hope House. Call Washington 2-1-1 for immediate referrals."
